<h1><%= @page_title = 'Share Your Story' %></h1>

<p>Most of the problems of the MTA are hidden away out of sight: ballooning debts, unnecessary administrators and missing progress can't be captured on camera in the subways.  But sometimes the evidence is in plain sight.  In those cases, it's up to us to collect and share this evidence to further the cause for change.  Perhaps it's a station agent sleeping because they have no real work to do, or yet another train too packed to enter.  Whatever it is, we appreciate your help in sharing your evidence, as shining a light on the problem is the first step toward correcting it.</p>

<p>To contribute your photos and videos, upload them to <%= link_to 'Flickr.com', 'http://flickr.com/' %> and tag them with "fixmta-evidence".  You can then view them below or <a href="http://www.flickr.com/search/?q=fixmta-evidence&amp;m=tags">browse them</a> on Flickr.</p>

